格式：
apt [options] command
apt-get [options] command
apt-get [options] install | remove pkg1 [pkg2 ...]
apt-get [options] source pkg1 [pkg2 ...]

COMMANDS:
list - list packages based on package names
search - search in package descriptions
show - show package details
install - install packages                      
reinstall - reinstall packages                 
remove - remove packages
autoremove - Remove automatically all unused packages
update - update list of available packages                            只检查，不更新，给出汇总报告
upgrade - upgrade the system by installing/upgrading packages         更新已安装的软件包  
full-upgrade - upgrade the system by removing/installing/upgrading packages
edit-sources - edit the source information file


apt-get命令：

可以进行安装、更新、移除软件包，apt-get是一个可以和APT(Advanced Package Tool)包管理系统交互的命令行工具，除此之外还有apt-cache，apt-config

apt命令：
apt包含了apt-get和apt-cache功能
apt有更多的输出和改进后的设计

--------sudo apt list --upgradable 查看可升级的包具体有哪些
--------sudo apt upgrade           更新已安装的软件包
--------sudo apt update            检查可以更新的软件包，给出汇总报告

建议能用apt就用，减少使用apt-get